{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"708","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"疫情衝擊經濟 ESG永續投資興起","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>文 郭信佑<span lang='EN-US'> 2020.06.02</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B0%B8%E7%BA%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87(1).jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 400px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>圖<span lang='EN-US'>/photoAC</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>今年新冠病毒疫情肆虐全球，國際知名機構包括貝萊德、晨星等亦緊盯各類資產的績效表現，統計全球在疫情期間著重<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>的指數或基金，可發現其表現優於大盤或同類型指數，台灣永續指數亦在疫情期間具有相對抗跌性，證明配置<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>和永續主題的投資組合，有助提高產品績效。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>隨著<span lang='EN-US'>Covid-19</span>疫情的蔓延，道瓊工業指數在第一季跌幅從高點至低點約<span lang='EN-US'>34%</span>，晨星公司研究指出在<span lang='EN-US'>57</span>個永續指數中，有<span lang='EN-US'>51</span>個指數的表現優於指標指數；同時，<span lang='EN-US'>MSCI</span>在其<span lang='EN-US'>17</span>個永續指數中有<span lang='EN-US'>15</span>個優於大盤同類指數的表現；台灣永續指數在疫情期間（<span lang='EN-US'>1/14~3/19</span>）的跌幅為<span lang='EN-US'>26.8%</span>，亦優於加權股價指數<span lang='EN-US'>28.6%</span>之跌幅。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>隨著國際基金著重<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>（環境，社會和治理）的永續投資趨勢的持續飆升，貝萊德新研究指出，在今年冠狀病毒引發的經濟低迷時期，大部分注重<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>的投資組合其表現都優於未注重<span lang='EN-US'>SEG</span>的投資組合，在動盪中尋求平衡投資組合時，現在越來越多投資者轉向注重企業永續發展的基金，而不是著重傳統基金。全球強調投資永續企業的開放式基金，在第一季度吸引約<span lang='EN-US'>405</span>億美元的新資產，增幅為<span lang='EN-US'>41</span>％，<span lang='EN-US'>ESG ETF</span>成為資金吸引機，今年以來（<span lang='EN-US'>2020/05</span>）金額達<span lang='EN-US'>72</span>億美元，已超過去年一整年。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>元大投信指出，因應公民意識興起，企業對<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>的重視提升，<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>相關標的也成為投資人關注焦點，<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>投資需具趨勢性、創新性、獲利性的三大條件。且在各國政府推動下，<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>因子已被多國退休基金列為投資標的篩選準則。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B0%B8%E7%BA%8C%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%872(1).jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 480px;' />&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>ESG</span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>主題<span lang='EN-US'>ETF</span>近二年成為全球投資主流。資料來源：彭博資訊、花旗、元大投信整理，<span lang='EN-US'>2020/05</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>觀察臺灣企業歷年營收獲利資料，落實<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>之企業，不僅經營效果逐年成長，且每股盈餘中位數更是年年攀升，有助<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>投資曲線穩步茁壯。元大投信於<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年發行全台第一檔元大臺灣<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>永續<span lang='EN-US'>ETF</span>（<span lang='EN-US'>00850</span>），追縱臺灣永續指數，至今，規模已增加<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>倍至新台幣<span lang='EN-US'>75.5</span>億元，受益人數亦翻倍至<span lang='EN-US'>6.17</span>萬人，儼然與元大台灣<span lang='EN-US'>50 ETF</span>（<span lang='EN-US'>0050</span>）、元大高股息<span lang='EN-US'>ETF</span>（<span lang='EN-US'>0056</span>）成為國人標配的國民<span lang='EN-US'>ETF</span>鐵三角。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>近來受新冠肺炎疫情影響，全球股市震盪加劇，若長線看好永續投資發展，可於市場動盪時逢低分批加碼具長線趨勢的<span lang='EN-US'>ESG</span>基金。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://ctee.com.tw/industrynews/financesmanage/278991.html</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-06-04","clk_count":"274"}},"__N_SSG":true}